During initial setup &susemgr; will request a product Registration Key. This key will be provided to you after purchasing the product. You can find your key located under your &scc; account. Login with your &scc; credentials or register for a new account. If you wish to run a test system (non-production) a 60 day evaluation key may be obtained. On the &susemgr; product page click TRY SUSE MANAGER. The evaluation key limits the number of systems that may be registered with SUSE Manager to 10.
